# SQL Daily Practice

Daily SQL problem solving — 2 problems every morning,
no exceptions. Part of an 8-month structured Data
Engineering upskilling program.

**Background:** Experience in airline revenue management
analytics. Applying SQL concepts directly to pricing,
demand forecasting, and booking data use cases.

---

## Structure

```
sql-practice/
├── leetcode/
│   ├── easy/       — filter, joins, aggregation
│   ├── medium/     — window functions, CTEs, subqueries
│   └── hard/       — complex joins, recursive CTEs
└── datalemur/
    ├── easy/
    └── medium/
```

