## Solution Template

Every `.sql` file follows this format:

```sql
-- Problem: [name]
-- Source: LeetCode #[number] / DataLemur
-- Difficulty: Easy / Medium / Hard
-- Pattern: [window function / CTE / join etc]
-- Date: YYYY-MM-DD
-- Time taken: X minutes

[solution here]

-- Learning: [what clicked]
-- Real world: [airline or health data connection]
```

